{"tid":694561,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（光輝歲月）今天只有殘留的軀殼，雲加光輝歲月，風雨中抱緊阿記","createTime":"2018-06-08T12:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T02:25:54.000Z","uid":36497,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d2035597a6f07f4e2aecb1bd3c48f7b22a9b5111","tid":694561,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/201102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F201102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d02c3e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐘聲響起雲加的訊號<br />\n在他生命裡 彷佛帶點唏噓<br />\n阿記領隊給他的意義<br />\n是一生奉獻 爭四鬥爭中<br />\n年月把擁有變做失去<br />\n疲倦的雲加帶著期望<br />\n<br />\n今天只有殘留的軀殼<br />\n雲加光輝歲月<br />\n風雨中抱緊阿記<br />\n一生經過徬徨的掙扎<br />\n雲加可改變未來<br />\n問誰又能做到<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd0ba46d5d77715dab17f64c49fce3e808cb303","tid":694561,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"樓主作得幾好  幫你推"},{"pid":"54e41e9e9e838a8d6fd0846fef2a1a509aa996ec","tid":694561,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cd0ba46d5d77715dab17f64c49fce3e808cb303","tid":694561,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"樓主作得幾好  幫你推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:15:24.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e7f5adcec7306e3f33bc906d65d6a080e04851","tid":694561,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cd0ba46d5d77715dab17f64c49fce3e808cb303","tid":694561,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"樓主作得幾好  幫你推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"比正評ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid